    "ExtensionModule composes Extension (this.extension)",
    "Extension composes ExtensionServiceState (this.service)",
    "Extension delegates to RuntimeModule (this.runtime — exports/import)",
    "ProxyContainer delegates to Container",
    "Container holds TeePromise as ready",
    "Container.emit triggers BaseService.__on_{event} handlers",
    "BootScriptService registered in Container via Kernel._install_modules()"
  ],
  "boot_sequence": [
    "1. Kernel.boot(): parse args, call _runtime_init(args) → creates RuntimeEnvironment",
    "2. Kernel.boot(): consoleLogManager.initialize_proxy_methods()",
    "3. Kernel.boot(): new Container() → new Context (root_context) → arun()",
    "4. Kernel._install_modules(): for each internal module: container.registerModule + module.install(context)",
    "5. Kernel._install_modules(): install_extern_mods_() → scan mod_paths → install_extern_mod_ + _run_extern_mod",
    "6. _run_extern_mod: assigns Extension config/name, loads module, registers event hooks (construct/preinit/init), calls ExtensionModule.install(context)",
    "7. ExtensionModule.install(): extension.emit('install') → services.registerService(uuid, ExtensionService, {state})",
    "8. Kernel._install_modules(): container.init() → service.run_as_early_as_possible, service.construct(), service.init() for all instances",
    "9. Kernel._install_modules(): services.ready.resolve()",
    "10. Kernel._boot_services(): container.emit('boot.consolidation') → emit('boot.activation') → emit('boot.ready')",
    "11. BootScriptService.__on_boot.ready(): reads boot script file → run_script(boot_json)"
  ],
  "key_patterns": [
    "Event-driven boot stages: boot.consolidation → boot.activation → boot.ready (Container.emit)",
    "Service auto-discovery: BaseService subclasses implement __on_{event} to subscribe to boot events",
    "DI Container: Container.registerService instantiates services with injected {services, config, my_config, name, args}",
    "TeePromise ready gate: Container.ready resolved after all services init; _boot_services awaits it",
    "External mod isolation: JS files in mod_paths are prepended with useapi globals, npm installed into mod_packages/",
    "Trait/implementor registry: Container.registerService tracks AdvancedBase trait implementors via get_implementors()",
    "ProxyContainer: wraps Container to override specific services locally while delegating others",
    "ConsoleLogManager singleton: proxies console.log/error/warn with decorator and post-hook pipeline"
  ],
  "important_notes": "Kernel is the single entry point; call Kernel.boot() to start. External mods (extensions) loaded from mod_paths, each gets its own Extension object and RuntimeModule. Container.init() supports parallel init via config.experimental_parallel_init. BootScriptService only activates if --boot-script CLI arg provided.",
